| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4931 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 568f9b0d-8fbb-5052-9f44-627e27412ea7"
